divs: Sighting Detailsi was in the front yard, in a lawn chair, it was just after hurricane dennis had hit the region. we were just talking and i alway star watch and that is when i noticed three stars in the shape of a triangle perfectly spaced. i thought they were cool and then realized they were moving in a western direction and told my friends to look and spotted them out for them and they were drinking so they couldnt focus but i hadnt been and watched them move to the west for about anohter minute or so then turned to speak to my friend and couldnt see them again. i first thought it to be stars. western move in almost a perfect line as they traveled. i have had ufo sightings after every hurricane we have had here in the panhandle and even after katrina.
